Package pt.ua.p2utils

Class LinkedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.ua.p2utils.LinkedList<E>

  • public class LinkedList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    A linked list implementation of the list ADT.

    It has efficient methods for adding elements to either end of the list and for removing an element from the begining of the list.

    Author:
    Luís Seabra Lopes, João Manuel Rodrigues
